of	O
the	O
frame	O
(	O
i	O
.	O
e	O
.	O
,	O
the	O
energy	O
of	O
the	O
frame	O
in	O
different	O
frequency	O
bands	O
)	O
of	O
the	O
digital	O
signal	O
125	O
(	O
and	O
the	O
corresponding	O
20	O
millisecond	O
time	O
period	O
of	O
the	O
analog	O
signal	O
110	O
that	O
represents	O
the	O
person	O
's	O
speech	O
)	O
.	O
Parameter	O
types	O
may	O
include	O
frequency	O
parameters	O
,	O
cepstral	O
parameters	O
,	O
and	O
signals	O
derived	O
from	O
