frequency	O
parameters	O
and	O
cepstral	O
parameters	O
.	O
Frequency	O
parameters	O
represent	O
the	O
content	O
of	O
the	O
speech	O
at	O
each	O
of	O
a	O
set	O
of	O
frequency	O
bands	O
and	O
are	O
generated	O
