description	O
of	O
how	O
utterances	O
are	O
received	O
and	O
stored	O
within	O
a	O
speech	O
recognition	O
system	O
,	O
see	O
U.S.	O
Pat	O
.	O
No.	O
5	O
,	O
027	O
,	O
406	O
,	O
entitled	O
"	O
