procedure	O
255	O
to	O
produce	O
from	O
the	O
vocabulary	O
205	O
a	O
list	O
of	O
words	O
that	O
are	O
likely	O
to	O
match	O
the	O
words	O
spoken	O
by	O
the	O
person	O
starting	O
at	O
a	O
particular	O
time	O
.	O
The	O
processor	O
then	O
uses	O
the	O
speech	O
recognition	O
procedure	O
250	O
to	O
compare	O
speech	O
models	O
for	O
those	O
words	O
to	O
the	O
digital	O
frames	O
representing	O
the	O
person	O
's	O
speech	O
.	O

The	O
vocabulary	O
205	O
includes	O
tens	O
of	O
thousands	O
of	O
words	O
.	O
The	O
number	O
of	O
