130	O
uses	O
the	O
pre-filtering	O
procedure	O
255	O
to	O
reduce	O
the	O
required	O
number	O
of	O
calculations	O
.	O
The	O
pre-filtering	O
procedure	O
performs	O
a	O
coarse	O
comparison	O
of	O
the	O
sequence	O
of	O
digital	O
frames	O
