considered	O
for	O
the	O
frame	O
,	O
then	O
the	O
processor	O
130	O
performs	O
a	O
detailed	O
match	O
to	O
determine	O
whether	O
the	O
word	O
was	O
likely	O
to	O
have	O
been	O
