corresponding	O
to	O
the	O
state	O
occurs	O
for	O
only	O
a	O
small	O
amount	O
of	O
time	O
and	O
a	O
relatively	O
small	O
value	O
when	O
the	O
sound	O
corresponding	O
to	O
the	O
state	O
occurs	O
for	O
a	O
large	O
amount	O
of	O
time	O
.	O

The	O
leaving	O
penalty	O
is	O
added	O
to	O
any	O
score	O
that	O
