and	O
to	O
the	O
length	O
of	O
the	O
phoneme	O
represented	O
by	O
the	O
node	O
to	O
which	O
the	O
state	O
belongs	O
.	O
For	O
example	O
,	O
the	O
duration	O
component	O
of	O
the	O
leaving	O
penalty	O
could	O
be	O
proportional	O
to	O
-	O
log	O
(	O
1/d.sub.avg	O
)	O
.	O
Thus	O
,	O
the	O
duration	O
component	O
of	O
the	O
