match	O
for	O
each	O
subnode	O
.	O
In	O
particular	O
,	O
the	O
processor	O
averages	O
the	O
next	O
four	O
frames	O
to	O
produce	O
a	O
smooth	O
frame	O
and	O
compares	O
the	O
smooth	O
frame	O
to	O
a	O
smooth	O
acoustic	O
model	O
for	O
the	O
phoneme	O
corresponding	O
to	O
each	O
subnode	O
to	O
generate	O
a	O
crude	O
acoustic	O
score	O
for	O
each	O
subnode	O
.	O
The	O
smooth	O
acoustic	O
model	O
is	O
context-independent	O
and	O
represents	O
the	O
first	O
smoothed	O
frame	O
of	O
the	O
phoneme	O
.	O
For	O
