the	O
processor	O
adds	O
the	O
crude	O
acoustic	O
score	O
and	O
a	O
portion	O
of	O
the	O
incremental	O
language	O
model	O
score	O
for	O
the	O
node	O
to	O
the	O
score	O
for	O
the	O
node	O
.	O
The	O
processor	O
eliminates	O
any	O
subnodes	O
for	O
which	O
the	O
crude	O
score	O
exceeds	O
a	O
second	O
