acoustic	O
match	O
for	O
the	O
remaining	O
subnode	O
(	O
s	O
)	O
.	O

The	O
processor	O
130	O
further	O
reduces	O
processing	O
by	O
associating	O
an	O
active	O
subnode	O
count	O
with	O
each	O
node	O
.	O
Thereafter	O
,	O
